### Step 3: Rewrite `src/templates/index.html` -- Merged Main Page

This is the biggest change. The new `index.html` combines:
1. **Status bar** from `index.html` Dashboard (compact version)
2. **Pipeline form** from `pipeline.html` (with location field added, template made optional)
3. **Search results table** from `search.html` (shown after search-only completes)
4. **Progress / confirmation / results** from `pipeline.html` (kept as-is)

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}

{% block title %}Maimai Assistant{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<!-- Compact status bar (replaces the full Dashboard) -->
<div id="status-bar" class="grid" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
    <div>
        <small>
